node.text: Wishing you all so much Merry from our front yard to yours!🎄
Celebrated the 9th graduating class at #OWLAG in South Africa this week! 🎓🎓🎓
Our 2019 Thanksgiving welcoming committee! Keeping our tradition of every time a new quest arrives.. we Sing em in! Happy Thanksgiving y’all. Hope there’s plenty of song and fun at your house!
In Milwaukee making Thanksgiving dinner with nieces. When there’s too many cooks in the kitchen kitchen... mimosas help! Cheers everyone.🥂
We’re kicking off 2020 in a big way! Follow our new wellness Instagram @ww.now where you’ll get all the latest updates on #Oprahs2020VisionTour. Hope to see you there!

One of my favorite things to do is rummage through @oprahmagazine’s book editor @leighhaberrr‘s office. She has all the latest books often before they’re published. What to my wondering eyes did appear.. a new faaaavorite thing! Tap the link in my bio to get it 📚 @michelleobama

‘Tis the season for Faaaaaavorite Things 2019! I’ve been searching all year long for the absolute must-have gifts and this time around I even got a little help from @ladygaga and @sarahjessicaparker. Now it’s my hope that these become some of YOUR favorite things. Happy holidays! Tap the link in my bio or head to oprahmag.com/oprah-favorite-things-2019 for the full list. @oprahmagazine
Watching TINA on Broadway with @tinaturner. Nothing like it. ELECTRIFYyyyying! See you at the Tonys @adriennelwarren! Swipe left to see what I’m talking about. #TinaBroadway @tinabroadway
This just happened to me in Central Park! It made me so happy to share my next @oprahsbookclub pick, “Olive, Again.” Janet and Fern, I’ll be calling you in two weeks! #ReadWithUs

My next @oprahsbookclub pick is going in a completely different direction than the last one: “Olive, Again” by Elizabeth Strout. As cranky as Olive is, she teaches us so much about loneliness, judgement, empathy, and loss…all the things that make us human. Tap the link in my bio to get a copy and follow @oprahsbookclub to join the conversation. Be ready to discuss with me starting 11/18! #ReadWithUs 🍂🍂🍂

Happy Sunday to you all. Don’t think I’ve ever seen burgundy peonies before. Wanted to share. Sending you the same blessings that were just sent to me from @jeffleatham . Card reads.. “Flowers, Just because  life is beautiful.” Here’s to a beautiful extra-hour of sleep, blessed week🌺🌺🌺🌺

It’s happening! My first @oprahsbookclub discussion with @tanehisipcoates is now live on @appletv. I was so excited to be with MY PEOPLE from all walks of life discussing one thing: our love for this glorious book. Stream it today by clicking on the AppleTV app. And if you don’t have Apple, don’t worry. Open up your browser, type in tv.apple.com and you’ll find it there. Did I also mention it’s free for the first 7 days? Happy streaming! #ReadWithUs

Moments before I stepped on stage to have my first @oprahsbookclub discussion for “The Water Dancer” with @tanehisipcoates and 234 book club members! I always wanted to be able to share the pleasures, the excitement, the tension, the drama a good book can bring you. And we’re finally doing it. Stream it tomorrow 11/1 on @appletv #ReadWithUs

Look who came for lunch...with his own book! @stephenathome. We both love the The Water Dancer. So many interesting insights. Join me at @oprahsbookclub where I’m discussing chapters 18-27 with members today. See y’all there 👋🏾 #ReadWithUs

Thank you @people for my story and the story of other women we know (and should know) who are making an impact around the world. Women like @AnaGraceProject (who’s supporting survivors of gun trauma), @tarajiphenson (who’s ending the stigma of mental illness), and @alexmorgan13, @mrapinoe, and @carlilloyd (who are championing equal pay). Available Friday 10/11 #WomenChangingTheWorld 📸: @ruvenafanador

Spent a day marinating in black excellence with these gorgeous, promising, young men at @morehouse1867. They honored me with roses, a song, and a portrait for a scholarship fund I set up 30 years ago. Can’t wait to see what they do with their future.

@tylerperry you built the biggest studio in America, one that can fit all the other Hollywood studios combined and still have room to spare. You’ve also created a dream of hope and possibility for everyone to know that no matter who you are or where you come from, you can always do better when you’re aligned with the Divine. Thank you for the naming of the soundstages. I love mine. #GloryToGlory #ImagineThis

I’m still in awe of that first sentence in The Water Dancer, which as you know was a full paragraph. Sharing over lunch with @lupitanyongo and @cynthiaerivo. Both who’ve portrayed enslaved women. Head to @oprahsbookclub for our full discussion 📚 #ReadwithUs
Such a great time at @UNCF event yesterday. A lot of Hat-ti-tude going on. Swipe left to see more hats from the beautiful Women Who Lead of Charlotte! #UNCFCharlotte

This is the man I wish was running for President of the USA. His decency prevails in all decision making. His 10 steps for leadership revealed in his new book #RideOfALifetime apply to every business and every life. Watch my conversation with Walt Disney CEO Bob Iger on @supersoul this Sunday 9/29 at 12|11c on @owntv and Facebook. Or listen to the podcast “SuperSoul Conversations” this Wednesday 10/2.

In the time it takes you to fry an egg, put on your gym shoes, or watch this @theellenshow clip you can instantly download a copy of my @oprahsbookclub pick on your phone or iPad. It’s that easy! Tap the link in my bio to get The Water Dancer by @tanehisipcoates! Can’t wait to talk to you about it. #ReadwithUs

Thanks for making The Water Dancer by @tanehisipcoates ALREADY #1! I applaud your good taste. I’ll be checking your comments at @oprahsbookclub for when you finish the first part. You’ll want to talk to me. 📚 #ReadwithUs
Long day that ended in the kitchen of @roosterharlem. Check out my stories for my day in NYC 🗽
An @apple moment in the Big Apple! My @oprahsbookclub pick “The Water Dancer” by @tanehisipcoates is already #1 on @applebooks! Tap the link in my bio to get a copy 📚🍏📚🍎📚 #ReadwithUs
Doing the happy dance because my new pick for @oprahsbookclub is finally out! And I got to kick things off on @cbsthismorning with @tanehisipcoates and @gayleking 💃🏾💃🏾 #ReadwithUs
